What is the marketing impact of short videos and user-generated content?
Revolutionary Change: The growing popularity of short films and user-generated content has brought about a revolutionary change in digital marketing.

Platform Influence: Platforms like TikTok, Instagram Reels, and Snapchat have played a significant role in transforming brand-audience engagement.

Efficient Communication: Short videos offer a concise and captivating structure, enabling efficient communication of messages to the audience.

User Engagement: Users sharing their works and experiences through user-generated content become potential brand ambassadors, amplifying brand engagement.

Authenticity Promotion: Both short videos and user-generated content encourage authenticity, altering the digital marketing landscape.

